      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration lovers! This vehicle is the perfect blank canvas for your next big project. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic work to return to its former glory, it offers a fantastic opportunity to build a car exactly how you want it. If you're looking for a rewarding challenge and a way to save a classic, this is the one for you!",
