    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality example that has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks, and all body panels are perfectly aligned. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather and trim appearing as if they just left the factory, free from any wear or odors. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having been maintained with an open checkbook and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle in pristine, original condition.",
